    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="好像也没什么可写的"><a href="#好像也没什么可写的" class="headerlink" title="好像也没什么可写的"></a>好像也没什么可写的</h3><h1 id="一"><a href="#一" class="headerlink" title="一"></a>一</h1><h2 id="参数传值"><a href="#参数传值" class="headerlink" title="参数传值"></a>参数传值</h2><ul><li>当调用对象，参数才会被分配空间</li></ul><h2 id="传值机制"><a href="#传值机制" class="headerlink" title="传值机制"></a>传值机制</h2><ul><li>传递的值不可以高于该参数的级别<br> 注： 数据类型的精度<figure class="highlight plaintext"><figcaption><span>Computer&#123;</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    int add(int x,int y)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        return x+y;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">public class Main &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Computer com =new Computer();//创建对象很重要</span><br><span class="line">        int m=100;</span><br><span class="line">        int n=200;</span><br><span class="line">        int result =com.add(m,n);</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(result);</span><br><span class="line">        result=com.add(120+m,n*10+8);</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(result);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="引用类型的传值"><a href="#引用类型的传值" class="headerlink" title="引用类型的传值"></a>引用类型的传值</h2><h5 id="（好困，这个地方好难呀）"><a href="#（好困，这个地方好难呀）" class="headerlink" title="（好困，这个地方好难呀）"></a>（好困，这个地方好难呀）</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><figcaption><span>Point&#123;</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    int radius;</span><br><span class="line">    Point(int radius)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        this.radius=radius;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">class Rect&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Point p;</span><br><span class="line">    Rect (Point r)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        p=r;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">public class Example2_0 &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Point pp = new Point(10);</span><br><span class="line">        Rect rect =new Rect(pp);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="可变参数"><a href="#可变参数" class="headerlink" title="可变参数"></a>可变参数</h2><ul><li></li></ul><h2 id="对象的组成"><a href="#对象的组成" class="headerlink" title="对象的组成"></a>对象的组成</h2>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
